<!-- HERO -->
<section style="background:#1c1917; color:#f2efe9; padding: 100px 24px 80px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto; text-align:center;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Nundah</p>
    <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(2.4rem, 5vw, 4rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.15; margin-bottom:1.5rem; color:#f2efe9;">
      Selling in Nundah, Brisbane.
    </h1>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1.05rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.7; color:#c9c4bc; max-width:580px; margin:0 auto 2.5rem;">
      Property sales in Nundah and Inner Brisbane.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1rem; justify-content:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <a href="/listings" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">View Current Listings</a>
      <a href="/property-worth" class="btn-gold" style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.85rem 2rem; text-decoration:none; display:inline-block;">What's your property worth?</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHY THIS AREA -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">Local Expertise</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.75rem;">Inner north character suburb with direct rail access and consistent buyer demand.</h2>
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      Nundah sits about eight kilometres north of the CBD, directly connected to the city and the airport via Nundah Station on the Doomben and Airport lines. It borders Clayfield and Ascot to the south, which creates a consistent spillover buyer dynamic: families and professionals who have been priced out of those suburbs, or who prefer more accessible entry into the inner north, find Nundah's character home streets a compelling alternative. The Sandgate Road commercial strip gives the suburb practical urban convenience, while the residential streets behind it have a settled character that newer buyers often underestimate until they see it in person.
    </p>
<!-- APPRAISAL FORM -->
<div style="background:#fff; border-left:4px solid #c4912a; padding:2rem 2rem 1.75rem; margin:2rem 0;">
  <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.72rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.18em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Free Appraisal</p>
  <h3 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.4rem; font-weight:300; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:1.25rem; line-height:1.25;">Find out what your Nundah home is worth.</h3>
  <form method="POST" action="https://formspree.io/f/xnjgedwp" style="display:flex; flex-direction:column; gap:0.75rem;">
  <input type="text" name="_gotcha" tabindex="-1" autocomplete="off" style="display:none" />
    <input type="hidden" name="_next" value="https://danielgierach.com/thank-you?from=suburb-appraisal" />
    <input type="hidden" name="_subject" value="Appraisal enquiry: Nundah" />
    <input type="hidden" name="_source" value="nundah" />
    <div style="display:grid; grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; gap:0.75rem;" class="suburb-form-grid">
      <input type="text" name="name" required placeholder="Your name" autocomplete="name"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#1c1917; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
      <input type="email" name="email" required placeholder="Email address" autocomplete="email"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#1c1917; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
    </div>
    <input type="text" name="property_address" required placeholder="Your Nundah address (street + number)"
      style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.88rem; padding:0.7rem 0.9rem; border:1px solid rgba(28,25,23,0.18); background:#faf9f7; color:#1c1917; outline:none; width:100%; box-sizing:border-box;" />
    <div style="display:flex; gap:0.75rem; align-items:center; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <button type="submit"
        style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.78rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.08em; text-transform:uppercase; background:#c4912a; color:#1c1917; padding:0.75rem 1.75rem; border:none; cursor:pointer; white-space:nowrap;">
        Request my free appraisal
      </button>
      <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:300; color:#78716c; margin:0; line-height:1.5;">Daniel will be in touch promptly. No pressure.</p>
    </div>
  </form>
</div>
<style>
  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .suburb-form-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>
<!-- END APPRAISAL FORM -->
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:1rem; font-weight:300; line-height:1.8; color:#4a4540; margin-bottom:1.25rem;">
      The Nundah buyer is often someone who has specifically researched the suburb and understands the value calculation it represents. Owner-occupiers looking for inner north character at a point below Clayfield and Ascot are consistent. Investors who understand the suburb's rental demand from professionals commuting via Nundah Station are active as well. When a well-presented character home in the right streets comes to market at a defensible price, competition follows quickly.
    </p>
    <div style="display:flex; gap:1.5rem; flex-wrap:wrap;">
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Nundah Specialist</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Inner North Brisbane</p>
      </div>
      <div style="flex:1; min-width:200px; background:#fff; padding:1.75rem; border-left:3px solid #c4912a;">
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.1rem; font-weight:400; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:0.4rem;">Character Homes, Rail Access</p>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.85rem; font-weight:300; color:#6b6560;">Clayfield and Ascot spill-over buyers</p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#78716c;margin-top:2rem;">Also selling in: <a href="/suburbs/clayfield" style="color:#c4912a;">Clayfield</a>, <a href="/suburbs/ascot" style="color:#c4912a;">Ascot</a>, <a href="/suburbs/windsor" style="color:#c4912a;">Windsor</a>, <a href="/suburbs/bowen-hills" style="color:#c4912a;">Bowen Hills</a>.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FAQ -->
<section style="background:var(--color-base, #f2efe9); padding:80px 24px;">
  <div style="max-width:800px; margin:0 auto;">
    <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.75rem; font-weight:700; letter-spacing:0.15em; text-transform:uppercase; color:#c4912a; margin-bottom:1rem;">FAQ</p>
    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.8rem); font-weight:300; line-height:1.2; color:#1c1917; margin-bottom:2.5rem;">Common questions about Nundah.</h2>
    <div style="display:flex; flex-direction:column;">
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What drives property values in Nundah Brisbane?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Nundah's character home market offers accessible inner north pricing relative to Clayfield and Ascot. Properties in the quieter streets away from Sandgate Road trade at a consistent premium over units near the commercial centre. Contact Daniel for a current appraisal on your specific property.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          How long does it take to sell a home in Nundah?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Well-presented Nundah character homes typically sell within 28 to 42 days when priced in line with recent comparable evidence. The suburb attracts motivated buyers from both owner-occupier and investor segments who are active throughout the year, which gives it a more even demand profile than some family-oriented suburbs further north.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="border-bottom:1px solid rgba(72,72,72,0.15); padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What is the lifestyle like in Nundah Brisbane?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Nundah has direct rail access to the CBD, the airport, and the Doomben line through Nundah Station. The Sandgate Road strip gives the suburb walkable access to cafes, restaurants and daily retail. The residential streets away from the corridor have a settled, low-density feel with established trees and a mix of character homes and post-war properties that give the suburb a genuinely local character.</p>
      </details>
      <details style="padding:1.25rem 0;">
        <summary style="font-family:var(--font-serif); font-size:1.05rem; cursor:pointer; color:#1c1917; list-style:none; display:flex; justify-content:space-between; align-items:center; gap:1rem;">
          What types of homes are in Nundah?
          <span style="color:#c4912a; font-size:1.4rem; flex-shrink:0;">+</span>
        </summary>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-sans); font-size:0.9rem; line-height:1.75; color:#4a4540; margin-top:0.75rem; padding-right:2rem;">Nundah has a mixed housing stock. Character homes including Queenslanders, workers cottages and post-war brick houses sit in the residential streets to the north and west of the station. A substantial apartment and unit layer is concentrated along the Sandgate Road corridor and near the station precinct. Character homes in well-positioned streets represent the primary owner-occupier target, while apartments offer the suburb's investment segment its entry point.</p>
      </details>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

